spec_data.Name: nodejs-pac-resolver
spec_data.Description:
This module accepts a JavaScript String of code, which is meant to be a
PAC proxy file, and returns a generated asynchronous `FindProxyForURL()`
function.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:42:28 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generates an asynchronous resolver function from a PAC file
